343
00:17:02,629 --> 00:17:05,349
And he kept asking me if you were fine.

344
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:09,268
As for Sher, he's Sun's sworn enemy.

345
00:17:09,269 --> 00:17:12,229
If his plot works, Sun will be in danger.

346
