I won't give you any chance to explain.

364
00:18:21,950 --> 00:18:22,950
Thank you, father.

365
00:18:33,310 --> 00:18:35,149
This is the letter that Gongsun Heng,

366
00:18:35,150 --> 00:18:36,748
